Now I've switched to using a rather nice full-screen MacVim session for my coding I find it quite disturbing to switch to other applications for taking notes. Without notes, my blogging suffers because I never have anything to write about.

Enter <a href="http://github.com/pedromg/vimblog.vim">vimblog</a>. Now I can wax lyrical about random crap without switching to another application. Lucky you!
